title: Big Brother UK S15E02 Power Trip Live Launch Pt2 1080i HDTV x264
description: Emma Willis hosts the second of two launch shows, ushering in another group of housemates to join last night's new contestants. There may also be a chance to see how Christopher, Danielle, Helen, Kimberly, Mark, Matthew, Pauline, Steven, Tamara and Winston are getting on 24 hours after moving in - although with the twists and turns Big Brother no doubt has up his sleeve, it may have been a bumpy ride for some. Twelve months ago, actor Michael joined the house to stir things up as the People's Puppet. This year, BB is promising a `power trip'. What does that mean for the hopefuls who have only just made their way down the famous staircase?
